Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.32,0:22:43.15,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}只为把你沮丧的泪水  轻轻吹干
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.80,0:22:50.20,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}口袋中 那小小的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.48,0:22:56.93,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}只盼你开怀一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.66,0:23:01.82,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}跑吧 跑吧 不断加速
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.16,0:23:05.54,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}即使发生不开心的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.70,0:23:08.94,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}也要在这条路上继续奔跑
